MERRILL MORTUARIES, Inc., a Corporation, Appellant, v. Ezra SHOEMAKER et al., Appellees. No. 7507. Circuit Court of Appeals, Ninth Circuit June 11, 1934 Hall & McCabe, of Great Falls, Mont, and Howard A. Johnson, of Butte, Mont, for appellees.

Before WILBUR, SAWTELLE, and GARRECHT, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Upon consideration of motion of appellees, ordered appeal herein dismissed for failure of appellant to file record and docket cause; mandate forthwith.
